#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.trojita.appdata.xml:7
msgid "Trojitá"
msgstr "Trojitá"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.trojita.appdata.xml:8
msgid "IMAP E-mail Client"
msgstr "IMAP e-posta bezeroa"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.trojita.appdata.xml:10
msgid ""
"Trojitá is an email program (\"client\") specialized in giving fast and "
"efficient access to mailboxes over the IMAP protocol. An IMAP mail server "
"stores messages and allows clients to fetch messages to the local computer "
"when asked for."
msgstr ""
"Trojitá e-posta programa (\"bezero\") bat da, IMAP protokoloaren gainean "
"postontzietara sarbide azkar eta eraginkorra ematen berezitua. IMAP posta "
"zerbitzari batek mezuak biltegiratzen ditu eta bezeroak eskatzen duenean "
"mezuak ordenagailu lokalera ekartzeko aukera ematen dio."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.trojita.appdata.xml:14
msgid ""
"It prioritizes efficiency, speed and open standards above other goals. "
"Trojitá also aims to be multi-platform, and functions well on everything "
"from big desktop computers to small cellphones. Trojitá is a stand-alone "
"program, not part of a \"personal information manager\" suite."
msgstr ""
"Beste helburuen gainetik, eraginkortasuna, abiadura eta estandar irekiak "
"lehenesten ditu. Trojitáren beste xedeetako bat plataforma-anitzekoa izatea "
"da, eta denean ondo dabil mahaigaineko ordenagailu handietatik telefono "
"mugikor txikietara. Trojitá programa autonomo bat da, ez da \"informazio "
"pertsonal kudeatzaile\" suite baten zati bat."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.trojita.appdata.xml:19
msgid "What could make Trojitá interesting for you:"
msgstr "Zer egin dezake Trojitá zuretzako interesgarria izatea:"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.trojita.appdata.xml:21
msgid "Very fast and robust IMAP core"
msgstr "IMAP nukleo oso azkar eta sendoa"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.trojita.appdata.xml:22
msgid "Standards compliance is a design goal"
msgstr "Estandarrak betetzea diseinuaren helburua bat da"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.trojita.appdata.xml:23
msgid "On-demand message list and body part loading (\"lazy loading\")"
msgstr ""
"Eskatu ahala mezu-zerrenda eta gorputz-atala zamatzea (\"zamatze nagia\")"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.trojita.appdata.xml:24
msgid "Offline IMAP support"
msgstr "Lerroz kanpoko IMAP euskarria"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.trojita.appdata.xml:25
msgid ""
"Support for bandwidth-saving mode aimed at mobile users with expensive "
"connection"
msgstr ""
"Banda zabalera aurrezteko moduaren euskarria, mugikorreko konexio garestia "
"duten erabiltzaileak helburu"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.trojita.appdata.xml:26
msgid ""
"IMAP over SSH -- instead of going over an SSL socket, the server could be "
"accessed via SSH"
msgstr ""
"SSH gaineko IMAP -- SSL hargune batetik joan ordez, zerbitzarira SSH bidez "
"sar liteke"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.trojita.appdata.xml:27
msgid "Safe and robust dealing with HTML mail"
msgstr "HTML postaren tratamendu segurua eta sendoa"

#. (itstool) path: screenshot/caption
#: org.kde.trojita.appdata.xml:37
msgid "Excessively quoted text is automatically collapsed"
msgstr "Aipu gehiegi dituen testua automatikoki tolesten da"

#. (itstool) path: screenshot/caption
#: org.kde.trojita.appdata.xml:41
msgid ""
"Encrypted and signed e-mail is supported, with status given in plain English"
msgstr ""
"Zifratutako eta sinatutako e-postaren euskarria du, egoera ingeles soilean "
"ematen delarik"
